   - **Prefix Max Array**: This array stores the maximum common prefix value from the start up to each index, enabling quick access to the max value in the left segment after removal.
   - **Suffix Max Array**: Similarly, this array stores the maximum common prefix value from each index to the end, enabling quick access to the max value in the right segment after removal.

